HEADWORD: Ironwork
<hw>I"ron*work`</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <def>Anything made of
iron; -- a general name of such parts or pieces of a building, vessel,
carriage, etc., as consist of iron.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

